  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\n## Why should this feature exist?\r\n\r\nSolidity supports `abi.encode` as well as `abi.EncodePacked` and `abi` package only exposes the `pack` method that returns output that matches `abi.encode` in solidity. \r\n\r\n\r\n## What are the use-cases?\r\n\r\nTo be able to do `abi.encodePacked` using the abi package in `go-ethereum`\r\n",
